            <description><![CDATA[【[我来了] <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%97%E7%8C%AB%E5%BC%8F%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E8%85%B0%E7%97%9B%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%80%E5%A5%97%E7%8C%AB%E5%BC%8F%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%BC%93%E8%A7%A3%E8%85%B0%E7%97%9B%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#一套猫式动作缓解腰痛#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%BD%A0%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%9A%E5%9D%90%E5%90%97%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%BD%A0%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%9A%E5%9D%90%E5%90%97%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#你真的会坐吗#</span></a>？久坐不动有可能导致腰肌劳损<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[单身狗]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/_/co_niuec-7d05bc992a.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>要注意养成良好的坐姿习惯：不塌腰、不靠着坐、不窝着坐、不跷二郎腿<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[二哈]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_erha-139d0e07bd.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 和卫一起试试这套猫式伸展运动，拉伸腰部肌肉，缓解酸痛👇🏻（央视新闻） <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4976805845598326" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hkmrf3jrbvj61yw13w7wh02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/MndegvP6lx08aN65fttu01041200OpQZ0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702356890&amp;ssig=kdLI%2B62JcW&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/cnGulab2lx08aN65BFC801041200oupw0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702356890&amp;ssig=kcPfbJGaCX&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/GdqI18FFlx08aN644vkQ01041200fsOy0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1702356890&amp;ssig=ePx9OY%2B9Zf&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4976805845598326" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
